             was indicted for that <rs id="t17931204-2-off5" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17931204-2-off5" type="offenceCategory" value="damage"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17931204-2-off5" type="offenceSubcategory" value="other"></interp>
               he, on the <rs id="t17931204-2-cd6" type="crimeDate">23d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931204-2-off5 t17931204-2-cd6"></join>, a mare, of the price of 5l. the goods and chattels of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17931204-2-victim65" type="victimName">
